textline.data: They system shall save the recorded
pressure values in FIFO inside flash
The system shall check if the
pressure is below a predefined threshold = 20 bar
The system shall inform the airplane
crew when the cabine has high pressure
the high pressure in the cabin
The system shall protect the airplane crew against high pressure
